Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
- CPSWorkflow = 3.4.0
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- new custom portlet to display threads
- stack is initialized when user does 'handle' transition.
- dashboard filtering on wf state excludes 'sent', 'trash' and 'closed'
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- 'directive' stack elt data is always rendered and translated
- better user feedback with french translations
- roadmap displayed actions and buttons correspond to what's allowed
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- added API to get thread infos from proxy
- One can explicitely exlude tokens from Select Filter Widget scopes.